cast.original_title: ドラゴンボールZ・絶望への反抗!!残された超戦士・悟飯とトランクス
cast.overview: It has been thirteen years since the Androids began their killing rampage and Son Gohan is the only person fighting back. He takes Bulma's son Trunks as a student and even gives his own life to save Trunks's. Now Trunks must figure out a way to change this apocalyptic future
cast.title: Dragon Ball Z: The History of Trunks

details.biography:
Nagasawa Nao (real name: Nagasawa Naomi, 長澤 直美) was born May 12, 1971 in Toyonaka, Osaka Prefecture, Japan, and grew up in Amagasaki, Hyogo Prefecture. She is a voice actress and was formerly represented by Aoni Production and Ken Production and is currently affiliated with Kekke Corporation. Her blood type is B.

Not to be confused with Nagasawa Nao (the pop star).
details.name: Naomi Nagasawa
